  "btn_help_commands": "📋 Commands",
  "btn_help_duels": "⚔️ Duels",
  "help_security_text": "🛡️ <b>Security Features</b>\n\n• Anti-Spam — detects repeated messages\n• Anti-Flood — limits rapid-fire messages\n• Anti-Raid — detects mass join attacks\n• Anti-Bot — blocks unauthorized bots\n• Anti-Link — blocks links from non-admins\n• Captcha — verifies new members\n• Lock System — restrict content types\n• Emergency Mode — full lockdown",
  "help_moderation_text": "⚖️ <b>Moderation Features</b>\n\n• /ban — permanently ban a user\n• /unban — remove a ban\n• /kick — remove a user from the group\n• /mute — restrict a user from sending messages\n• /unmute — restore a user's ability to send\n• /warn — issue a warning (auto-action at max)\n• /unwarn — remove a warning\n• /notes — add notes to a user\n• /history — view user action history",
  "help_economy_text": "💰 <b>Economy Features</b>\n\n• Daily/weekly/monthly rewards\n• Wallet (cash + bank)\n• Deposit and withdraw\n• Transfer coins to others\n• Transaction history\n• Leaderboard rankings",
  "help_games_text": "🎮 <b>Games</b>\n\n• 🎲 Dice — bet and roll\n• 🎡 Spin Wheel — multiple multipliers\n• ✊ Rock Paper Scissors\n• 🃏 Card Battle — higher card wins\n• 🔢 Number War\n• 💣 Minesweeper\n• 🎰 Roulette",
  "help_commands_text": "📋 <b>Admin Commands</b>\n\n/ban @user [reason] — ban\n/unban @user — unban\n/kick @user [reason] — kick\n/mute @user [time] [reason] — mute\n/unmute @user — unmute\n/warn @user [reason] — warn\n/unwarn @user — remove warn\n/notes @user — user notes\n/history @user — action history",
  "help_duels_text": "⚔️ <b>Duels & Tournaments</b>\n\n• Challenge users with /duel @user [amount]\n• Loser pays the winner\n• Win streaks give bonus rewards\n• Tournament rankings tracked globally",
  "help_gameslist_text": "🎮 <b>Game List</b>\n\n1. 🎲 Smart Dice — multiple modes\n2. 🎡 Luck Wheel — multiplier spins\n3. 🃏 Card Battle — highest card wins\n4. 🔢 Number War — highest number wins\n5. ✊ Rock Paper Scissors — classic!\n6. 💣 Minesweeper — reveal safe cells\n7. 🎰 Roulette — test your luck",
  "help_achievements_text": "🏅 <b>Achievements</b>\n\nEarn 100+ achievements across 5 categories:\n\n🎮 Games — wins, streaks, mastery\n💰 Economy — savings, spending, records\n📊 Activity — messages, rewards, levels\n🤝 Community — referrals, reputation\n🎪 Events — tournaments, seasonal challenges",
